{"tid":988360,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［語言遊戲］有冇啲咩paradox你哋覺得有趣/有意義？","createTime":"2019-01-20T04:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T07:30:38.000Z","uid":210794,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7b184adac9521f353c762adbac15475a90160d82","tid":988360,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:04:08.000Z","msg":"拋吓磚先：<br />\n1. 黑格爾名句：「我哋喺歷史入面學到嘅就係我哋喺歷史入面乜都學唔到」「(We learn from history that we do not learn from history. &mdash; Hegel)<br />\n2.呢個世界唯一唔變嘅就係呢個世界永遠都變緊。<br />\n（變幻原是永恆）<br />\n3. I know one thing: I know nothing.&mdash;Socrates"},{"pid":"d0557e7f282307e6ff3e5bf95adef1d64e988aeb","tid":988360,"uid":144409,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"7b184adac9521f353c762adbac15475a90160d82","tid":988360,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:04:08.000Z","msg":"拋吓磚先：<br />\n1. 黑格爾名句：「我哋喺歷史入面學到嘅就係我哋喺歷史入面乜都學唔到」「(We learn from history that we do not learn from history. &mdash; Hegel)<br />\n2.呢個世界唯一唔變嘅就係呢個世界永遠都變緊。<br />\n（變幻原是永恆）<br />\n3. I know one thing: I know nothing.&mdash;Socrates"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"你明唔明咩係paradox<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%82%96%E8%AE%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E6%2582%2596%25E8%25AE%25BA&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a9dc8a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%82%96%E8%AE%BA</a>"},{"pid":"ebe6b65ca0ca3bcf201209b7d13592907d560696","tid":988360,"uid":14566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:43:31.000Z","msg":"If you have to ask, you will never know"},{"pid":"ac31b2d524cac9427fa62f3cb8678ca8eee04a8f","tid":988360,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"d0557e7f282307e6ff3e5bf95adef1d64e988aeb","tid":988360,"uid":144409,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"7b184adac9521f