g/zh-tw/%E6%82%96%E8%AE%BA</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"又真又假有矛盾，好似一個loop咁咪算paradox⋯⋯"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"有一個命題A，稱為悖論命題。<br />\n有一個邏輯系統L，稱為相關系統。<br />\n有一組命題E, 稱為背景命題。背景命題都是相關係統中的真命題。相關係統被簡化為背景命題，背景命題成為悖論證明的依據。<br />\n相關係統存在兩個證明可以獲得悖論命題A的真值，其中一個證明A為真，而另一個證明A為假，從而出現矛盾。"},{"pid":"da3bb8d8074543190c27fea010707960809336cd","tid":988360,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f2e9552d9446a74a6f02328f0b33ab7ea2ceb7f","tid":988360,"uid":144409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ac31b2d524cac9427fa62f3cb8678ca8eee04a8f","tid":988360,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"d0557e7f282307e6ff3e5bf95adef1d64e988aeb","tid":988360,"uid":144409,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"你明唔明咩係paradox<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%82%96%E8%AE%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E6%2582%2596%25E8%25AE%25BA&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a9dc8a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%82%96%E8%AE%BA</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"又真又假有矛盾，好似一個loop咁咪算paradox⋯⋯"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"有一個命題A，稱為悖論命題。<br />\n有一個邏輯系統L，稱為相關系統。<br />\n有一組命題E, 稱為背景命題。背景命題都是相關係統中的真命題。相關係統被簡化為背景命題，背景命題成為悖論證明的依據。<br />\n相關係統存在兩個證明可以獲得悖論命題A的真值，其中一個證明A為真，而另一個證明A為假，從而出現矛盾。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:39:36.000Z","msg":"咁我講嗰類句子叫咩⋯⋯認真問。<br />\n我見呢啲都算：<br />\n<a href=\"https://examples.yourdictionary.com/examples-of-paradox.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexamples.yourdictionary.com%2Fexamples-of-paradox.html&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2c729b88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://examples.yourdictionary.com/examples-of-paradox.html</a>"},{"pid":"3e26aee6421b3d83