ore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f726efe51843ed39ee99496c1229f73b3c1a62e","tid":988360,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5f57334be66f28e374aa7be03db3cf4fe58a5c7","tid":988360,"uid":69779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"Simpson's paradox<br />\nRao's paradox<br />\n我覺得有practical application嘅paradox最有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n《莊子．天下篇》好多依類弔詭語言<br />\n古希臘都好多，比如克里特悖論"},{"pid":"47e57b44101ef1968d3658a3d45cc6087f41db62","tid":988360,"uid":78907,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"If u are nothing without this suit, u shouldn&rsquo;t have it"},{"pid":"16cd07ceeb0811d2dc0a469b7ddfbb065aecf2da","tid":988360,"uid":61577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T07:30:38.000Z","msg":"我呢句講緊大話"}]}